OL,3,CGuernsey's Martin Lewis? Mums set up
OL,4,Cwebsite to save others money
OL,6,FTwo Guernsey mothers have set up an
OL,7,Fonline community to support families
OL,8,Fstruggling with the cost of living.
OL,10,FKat Gillespie and Sarah de Carteret
OL,11,Fcreated the free public site
OL,12,F'Supersavvysavers' in the hope of
OL,13,Fhelping local people find the latest
OL,14,Foffers, deals and discounts at shops
OL,15,Fand supermarkets.
OL,17,FAfter several discussions about price
OL,18,Finflations and where to buy items
OL,19,Ffrom, the pair decided to share what
OL,20,Fthey found on social media and a
OL,21,Fbespoke website.
