OL,3,CGuernsey's Martin Lewis? Mums set up
OL,4,Cwebsite to save others money
OL,6,FTheir Facebook page now has around
OL,7,F2,500 followers with tips and cost-
OL,8,Fsaving tricks plus price comparisons
OL,9,Fon essential items for all the major
OL,10,Fsupermarkets.
OL,12,FKat is particularly worried about
OL,13,Ffamilies trying to make ends meet.
OL,15,FShe explains: "We're feeling it and I
OL,16,Fdon't know how single parents are
OL,17,Fsurviving at the moment, no idea.
