OL,3,CGuernsey's Martin Lewis? Mums set up
OL,4,Cwebsite to save others money
OL,6,F"People are finding it difficult
OL,7,Fbecause everything's gone up - the
OL,8,Fhousehold bills, electricity,
OL,9,Finsurance has gone sky high and
OL,10,Finterest rates paying the mortgage.
OL,11,FThat's before you look at the weekly
OL,12,Fshop."
OL,14,FSarah believes that collaboration is
OL,15,Fkey as supermarkets want to help those
OL,16,Fin need.
OL,18,FShe says: "They are always liking and
OL,19,Fcommenting on the posts that we put
OL,20,Fout there and emailing us.
