OL,3,CGuernsey's Martin Lewis? Mums set up
OL,4,Cwebsite to save others money
OL,6,F"They want to work with us and all
OL,7,Fgenuinely seem to want to be able to
OL,8,Fput their prices down and help as much
OL,9,Fas they can, and I think that will
OL,10,Fhappen.
OL,12,F"We've been checking prices since
OL,13,FApril and already there's been drops
OL,14,Famong those 25 essentials."
OL,16,FChrissie Salmon, Team Leader at Shiloh
OL,17,FChurch, says their foodbank has seen
OL,18,Fan increase in demand for uniforms and
OL,19,Fbaby outfits alongside food.
