OL,3,CGuernsey's Martin Lewis? Mums set up
OL,4,Cwebsite to save others money
OL,6,FShe explains: "The need has definitely
OL,7,Fchanged over the last 12 months as
OL,8,Fpeople have been struggling with
OL,9,Finterest rates going up.
OL,11,F"It is a surprise and the challenge is
OL,12,Fgreater than it's ever been. We have
OL,13,Fpeople who maybe just visit us once
OL,14,Fbecause they have a week of crisis, a
OL,15,Fweek where they need to.
OL,17,F"There are those who come regularly
OL,18,Fbecause they're just struggling to
OL,19,Fmake ends meet but it is from all
OL,20,Fwalks of life that we're seeing
OL,21,Fpeople."
